data.description: This beautiful home is in the heart of Denham Springs, near shopping, restaurants, and the popular antique village. One of a kind, beautifully updated with a glamour kitchen, huge living room, and lots of special features throughout. Open floorplan with granite and under cabinet lighting, custom cabinets, exposed beams, and upgraded appliances plus refrigerator. Spacious laundry/mudroom. Beautiful new laminate and tile flooring throughout. Lots of natural light and neutral colors! As a Bonus, you get a 2-year-old Hut Tub. See all the gorgeous details in person! Schedule your showing today!!!! Fantastic location, Livingston Parish schools, and flood zone X!
